{"tid":1559091,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我終於明點解其他國家嘅人唱國歌會激動","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T17:27:48.000Z","uid":33540,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c21ffdba5b15eff733af4c29e7820862b5e737b","tid":1559091,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"講真之前細個唱義勇軍進行曲都係hea9住唱唔知唱黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係見其他國家嘅人唱國歌都好嚴肅or少少激動<br />\n我心諗洗唔洗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係宜家香港有終於有自己嘅國歌加上個mv<br />\n<br />\n呢三個月發生嘅事跟住啲音樂係我嗰腦到閃過<br />\n每次聽都想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於開始理解點解其他國家唱國歌會激動<br />\n我諗呢啲就係歸屬感<br />\n<br />\n多謝爸絲寫左一首代表到香港嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n終有一日可以一齊係煲底除面罩唱國歌</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1611a59a3f557d0b8ffcd88211e52481eb75d9f2","tid":1559091,"uid":33540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"真係每次聽都想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94b7e8416b2e37223e535da7ced94e6ca5e37e4","tid":1559091,"uid":33540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"希望啲人唔好再話歌係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c078bd407d5b432d6e8287a50307af57fd2bc3d8","tid":1559091,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"頭先係大球場唱真係眼濕濕"},{"pid":"3ba13582eef76be0b903f45b5f1d2622cca16226","tid":1559091,"uid":33540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c078bd407d5b432d6e8287a50307af57fd2bc3d8","tid":1559091,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"頭先係大球場唱真係眼濕濕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"個mv都真係功不可沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49b24a7ef421078417870eaa2f4e8ab39494178","tid":1559091,"uid":61697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"首歌好有代表性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4418866a075e620696ad4bc7d3c56a22cb07fdac","tid":1559091,"uid":305017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"每次聽都好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cbcc7359d25e49522dc075894e6bd213150148","tid":1559091,"uid":35592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"香港人終於有國民身份認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3933fffe83eb16c9a19dd31c3aab3cb9aef6ddd","tid":1559091,"uid":280771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"呢幾日首歌一直喺腦海度loop<br />\n早幾日去發夢 發到一半響起左呢隻歌同周公一齊唱，啲眼淚係自己湧出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d8005713d62f6b58eeb06cb4a76583d9d4ba86","tid":1559091,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"國民教育講得岩<br />\n聽國歌真係會流眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9865c3832db40ff77011b6820ed814d9a0807c52","tid":1559091,"uid":302382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:27:48.000Z","msg":"同行兒女 為正義 時代革命 <img s